
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-zhang-mif-connection-manager-arena-00.txt'>
    <title>"Multi-interface Network Connection Manager in Arena Platform", Yan Zhang, Tao Sun, Hua Chen</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-zhang-mif-connection-manager-arena-00.txt</link>
    <description>This document presents a "Connection Manager" model implemented in the platform Arena, a mobile OS based on Linux. The introduction of Connection Manager brings two major benefits in Arena. First, it logically decouples the underlining connection approach with the connection management. Second, it plays a central role which executes the policy of OS, especially for multiple interfaces.</description>
    <dc:date>2009-02-26T23:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
